TitleEnglish: Go! Anpanman: The Pyramid of the Rainbow
SummaryEnglish: In the land of the pyramids, the Rainbow Prince turns everyone into pyramids! Can Anpanman find snow and water, the weakness of the Rainbow Prince, and stop him before it's too late?
Aliases: Sore ike! Anpan man niji no piramiddo
Sore Ike! Anpanman: Niji no Pyramid
